<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>2) Evade:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> I agree on what Vasagh already said. I think our evade doesn't scale because we share it with other realms main tanks. Maybe it doesn't scale to keep Buff+Evade+Chain/Scale = Buff+Plate. From tests Evade I+Chain is 2-3% worse than other light tanks Evade III+Studded. As it's now evade issues are:<br>
<br>
