<br>
You get stunned, which interrupts your cast. If you purge then subsequent hits do not interrupt for the duration of MOC. So a stun is a one-time interrupt for moc with purge. Your proposed change to dirty tricks would have effect for the entire duration as there's no immunity.<br>
